snippet.title: Hell Is Others [PC] Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Hell Is Others is a rogue-like meets farming shooter set in a city where blood and bullets are currency.


More details here: 


Hell Is Others launches on Steam Early Access for in 2021 with a full launch scheduled for Winter 2021.
